        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 6: HTR1D colocalises with substance P in 5-HT1D-IR neurons.\nFigure 7: Immunoelectron microscopy displays localisation of HTR1D on DCVs in the synapse of the lumbar dorsal horn.\n\nNote: Controls for secondary antibody specificity was checked by immunostaining tissue without the primary antisera or adding the appropriate antigen peptide. The specificity for the primary antibody wasn't checked.. Experimental description: Sprague Dawley rats were used" ;
